description: This preview features 8 pages of breathtaking action, as the legendary swashbuckler of the seven seas finds himself a prisoner, and forced to battle gladiator style by the strange and mysterious denizens of the Red Planet. Written by Greg Thompson (Hero Camp) and illustrated by Jeff "Chamba" Cruz this preview sets the stage for a grand adventure, the likes which have never been seen before. Includes a forward by Ray Harryhausen.
